<% data = adapter.panel_data %>
## Polymarket Neg-Risk Adapter

Multi-outcome resolution adapter on Polygon. Decomposes multi-outcome
events into binary subquestions that get resolved independently.

<% if data[:groups].present? %>
<% data[:groups].each do |event_name, items| %>
### <%= event_name %>

<% items.each do |item| %>
- <% if item.market_id %>market `<%= item.market_id.to_s[0..9] %>…`<% end %><% if item.question_id %> · question `<%= item.question_id.to_s[0..9] %>…`<% end %><% if !item.outcome.nil? %> · outcome **<%= item.outcome %>**<% end %><% if item.payouts.any? %> · payouts [<%= item.payouts.join(", ") %>]<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% else %>
_No multi-outcome resolution activity in the last ~3h._
<% if data[:unavailable_events].any? %>
Probed events not in this contract's ABI: <%= data[:unavailable_events].keys.join(", ") %>.
<% end %>
<% end %>
